{"tid":851604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴士車禍檢討】詳細意外紀錄無公開　運輸署長：公眾未必有興趣","createTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T10:31:22.000Z","uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df80134ed14c149db333baf0bdf2cf1ed117dffa","tid":851604,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"香港專營巴士服務獨立檢討委員會今日（6日）下午繼續召開第十六節聽證會，由運輸署代表出席作供。<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦運輸局現時會詳細列明每一宗巴士意外資料，被問到香港能否效法相關做法，運輸署署長陳美寶回應表示，香港目前未能做到，且公眾未必有興趣閱讀相關資料。有關說法隨即被委員會主席倫明高反駁指，公眾未必有興趣，但現時資料未有公開，根本沒有機會閱讀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942848/org/a19e8930f2b6f87b0daa3b2bcec49fb2.jpg/loYzi0hEPt38p3fJT6e8LZa3SrsS2k7lTOMYAEzjGAA?v=w1280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1942848%2Forg%2Fa19e8930f2b6f87b0daa3b2bcec49fb2.jpg%2FloYzi0hEPt38p3fJT6e8LZa3SrsS2k7lTOMYAEzjGAA%3Fv%3Dw1280&d=YiRPLJSXIFINIeAtdkTNU10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=59c6b3d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942848/org/a19e8930f2b6f87b0daa3b2bcec49fb2.jpg/loYzi0hEPt38p3fJT6e8LZa3SrsS2k7lTOMYAEzjGAA?v=w1280</a><br />\n<br />\n根據九巴提交運輸署的文件，當中提及有超過5成乘客因巴士煞車而導致失去平衡，有近37%的乘客更因碰撞而受傷。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n委員會代表大律師陳政龍指出，根據九巴提交運輸署的文件，當中提及有超過5成乘客因巴士煞車而導致失去平衡，有近37%的乘客更因碰撞而受傷。運輸署署長陳美寶指出，當局十分關注巴士乘客於車廂失去平衡的情況，亦於2013年就專營權續期時，曾與巴士公司交換承諾信件，要求巴士公司於巴士樓梯增加雙排扶手，以免乘客下樓梯時，在上層巴士跌倒滾下。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席倫明高問及，運輸署就巴士煞車引致乘客失去平衡，會如何監督巴士公司，以及採取什麼行動。陳美寶表示，正要求專營巴士公司提交黑盒數據，以檢視巴士車長有否行為不當，如突然加速、減速的情況。<br />\n<br />\n而公開巴士意外的資料，倫敦運輸局現時以表列方式，清楚列明每一宗巴士發生意外，所涉及的巴士路線、日期、傷者的個人資料等，且每一季度巴士公司都會就數據作出分析及比較。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942860/org/863bde1a26e0e58f12f6963da77c2f9a.jpg/FsZirsd0cXkfhvvtHMTWVDGAFhGAWBRkDQUc1A0FHNQ?v=w1280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1942860%2Forg%2F863bde1a26e0e58f12f6963da77c2f9a.jpg%2FFsZirsd0cXkfhvvtHMTWVDGAFhGAWBRkDQUc1A0FHNQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&d=YiRPLJSXIFINIeAtdkTNU10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=14607cdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942860/org/863bde1a26e0e58f12f6963da77c2f9a.jpg/FsZirsd0cXkfhvvtHMTWVDGAFhGAWBRkDQUc1A0FHNQ?v=w1280</a><br />\n<br />\n陳美寶指出，相關資料並未向公眾公開，又指公眾未必有興趣取閱相關資料。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n委員會代表大律師陳政龍問及運輸署能否效法倫敦做法，陳美寶指香港目前未能做到，惟會記錄致命的交通意外，所涉及的行車路線及受害人資料，而相關資料並未向公眾公開，又指公眾未必有興趣取閱。倫明高反駁指，公眾未必有興趣，但現時資料未有公開，根本沒有機會閱讀。陳美寶解釋，正研究如何公開資料，會於2019年向倫敦運輸局參考相關做法。"},{"pid":"72eeaa2dba798f03745c28768dc87628c8ff59f0","tid":851604,"uid":104454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942848/org/a19e8930f2b6f87b0daa3b2bcec49fb2.jpg/loYzi0hEPt38p3fJT6e8LZa3SrsS2k7lTOMYAEzjGAA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1942848%2Forg%2Fa19e8930f2b6f87b0daa3b2bcec49fb2.jpg%2FloYzi0hEPt38p3fJT6e8LZa3SrsS2k7lTOMYAEzjGAA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=821bf296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據九巴提交運輸署的文件，當中提及有超過5成乘客因巴士煞車而導致失去平衡，有近37%的乘客更因碰撞而受傷。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1942860/org/863bde1a26e0e58f12f6963da77c2f9a.jpg/FsZirsd0cXkfhvvtHMTWVDGAFhGAWBRkDQUc1A0FHNQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1942860%2Forg%2F863bde1a26e0e58f12f6963da77c2f9a.jpg%2FFsZirsd0cXkfhvvtHMTWVDGAFhGAWBRkDQUc1A0FHNQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=23504def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳美寶指出，相關資料並未向公眾公開，又指公眾未必有興趣取閱相關資料。（資料圖片）"},{"pid":"b4815f111179cd2e3d51dca492c318fd9a0c73ae","tid":851604,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"我對屌你老母就真係無興趣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f2952faf47a23271c2859cc54ba099adb23b7d","tid":851604,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"巴士迷就係公眾之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b0d3942b95d1429bdd253d00b15a462b15e25c","tid":851604,"uid":46896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"喂起碼啲巴膠同區佬會有興趣"},{"pid":"111a4124a5b92df1f7d9d8e65b6c48592942c9e1","tid":851604,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"有興趣 公開得未？"},{"pid":"bd76514cef0071ffba05824d20924769e4fc25cd","tid":851604,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"成日屈尻公眾無興趣，咩撚野理由黎？"},{"pid":"0ff2b617cb64d8921d9a037774d41fd2bc994dc9","tid":851604,"uid":151071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"廢老wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0364ae7d9fdafd8f2aa510815af2178e0d139d44","tid":851604,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"沙中線學下人點講喇 <br />\n無興趣呀"},{"pid":"72130420cb3b54d43adf6aeea30c8cd459635a72","tid":851604,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"你點撚知我無興趣？"},{"pid":"9707a386dc87ef34b842761267cd4d27f63879cd","tid":851604,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"Btw 依家啲巴士上層無曬扶手 一開車但係未行到個位既時候都唔知扶邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ed64cddc3bafd4ae620072bb19528ee25d4c43","tid":851604,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"葉劉上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}